Delete Your Account — Be A World Champion

To request deletion of your account and associated data:

1. Email beaworldchampion.app@gmail.com from the email address linked to your account.
2. Subject line: "Account Deletion Request"
3. Include your account email address.

What we delete:
- Your account (email, username, profile)
- Predictions, league memberships, and leaderboard data tied to your account

What we may retain (up to 12 months unless law requires longer):
- Purchase records for tax/legal compliance
- Aggregated/anonymous analytics

Third-party services (Firebase, AdMob, RevenueCat) may retain data per their own policies.

We will confirm deletion within 30 days.
